{"tid":549951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好懷念電腦遊戲百花齊放嘅時代","createTime":"2018-02-04T08:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T09:55:02.000Z","uid":169392,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"63aca64affe49b92d277a6159f3d02efbe8b009d","tid":549951,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣好慶幸自己出生在電腦遊戲最輝煌嘅時代？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n彩虹冒險，巨商，古惑仔online，吞食天地，墨香，瑪奇，魔力，勁舞團，跑，亂，魔獸爭霸（信長，守女...), cs, hp ... 等等數之不盡<br />\n<br />\n果種可以一齊合力/競技嘅感覺，<br />\n而家已經唔會搵得番。<br />\n<br />\n電腦game對比而家啲濕鳩手機game真係高唔知幾多班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:90後＋所有手機game 加埋玩唔超過1粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfad2387d0a6df725accbb8aef3a8aa96f89d31a","tid":549951,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f033390b059f7ef5487e156ca4f066b620011b45","tid":549951,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pubg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPubg雖然唔係大逃殺始祖，<br />\n但佢的確推動番大眾對電腦遊戲嘅熱潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313c823ec492e32d0384ddb527b1fed97acb0e72","tid":549951,"uid":37713,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"90後又扮老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過都真係幾掛住啲mmorpg<br />\n個時識朋友好容易<br />\n而家就算有返同類型game 都係各有各玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dc2a8fee690031aa3eabe5536c1cc627b90064","tid":549951,"uid":169392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90後又扮老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n